#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rkward; is meant to be(come) an easy to use graphical frontend to the "
"powerful &R; language for statistical computing. Since &R; is a full "
"featured programming language, &rkward; will never be able to offer a "
"complete GUI for everything in &R;. However, &rkward; strives to make common "
"task simple, to provide an easy entry point for newcomers, while at the same "
"time, transparent access to the full power of the underlying &R; language is "
"provided for advanced users."
msgstr ""
"&rkward; शक्तिशालिनः &R; सांख्यिकीयगणनायाः कृते भाषा। यतः &R; पूर्णविशेषतायुक्ता "
"प्रोग्रामिंगभाषा अस्ति, &rkward; &R;मध्ये सर्वस्य कृते कदापि सम्पूर्णं GUI प्रदातुं न शक्ष्यति "
"। तथापि &rkward; सामान्यं कार्यं सरलं कर्तुं, नव आगन्तुकानां कृते सुलभं प्रवेशबिन्दुं प्रदातुं, "
"तत्सहकालं च, अन्तर्निहितस्य &R; उन्नतप्रयोक्तृणां कृते भाषा प्रदत्ता अस्ति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &rkward;"
msgstr "&rkward इत्यस्य उपयोगेन;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most documentation is available from inside &rkward; itself by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in &rkward; from the menu, <emphasis>not</emphasis> in this "
"document."
msgstr ""
"अधिकांशं दस्तावेजीकरणं अन्तः एव उपलभ्यते &rkward; स्वयं &rkward; मेनूतः, अस्मिन् दस्तावेजे "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A useful guide to getting started with &rkward; is <ulink url=\"https://"
"rkward.kde.org/User_Documentation\">User Documentation Section in the "
"&rkward; wiki</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&rkward; इति <ulink url=\"https://rkward.kde.org/User_Documentation"
"\">उपयोक्तृदस्तावेजविभागः &rkward; विकि</ulink> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please go there for an introduction to &rkward;, and contact us, if you can "
"help with creating user documentation."
msgstr ""
"कृपया &rkward;, परिचयार्थं तत्र गच्छन्तु, अस्माभिः सह सम्पर्कं कुर्वन्तु, यदि भवान् "
"उपयोक्तृदस्तावेजनिर्माणे सहायतां कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Developer's Guide to &rkward;"
msgstr "विकासकस्य मार्गदर्शिका &rkward;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rkward; can be extended without the need to recompile using plugins. "
"Extensive documentation on this should be included with &rkward; in DocBook "
"format, and is available in &HTML; format <ulink url=\"https://api.kde.org/"
"doc/rkwardplugins\">here</ulink>. (TODO: figure out, how to include this in "
"the documentation)."
msgstr ""
"&rkward; प्लगिन्स् इत्यस्य उपयोगेन पुनः संकलनस्य आवश्यकतां विना विस्तारितुं शक्यते । अस्य "
"विषये विस्तृतं दस्तावेजं &rkward; DocBook प्रारूपेण, तथा च &HTML; प्रारूपं <ulink url="
"\"https://api.kde.org/doc/rkwardplugins\">अत्र</ulink> । (TODO: figure out, "
"एतत् दस्तावेजीकरणे कथं समाविष्टं कर्तव्यम्)।"

